<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (nfrḥ byk yạ msyḥnạ yạ gẖạly .. dy qlwbnạ btgẖny lyk
 frḥk nwr lynạ lyạly .. hllwyạ mjdaⁿạ lyk)2
 1- (sẖkr wḥmd wạftkẖạr .. dh ạ̹ḥsạsnạ lyk yạ yswʿ
 mdywnyn lạsmk yạ bạr .. ạ̉sẖbʿtnạ mn bʿd ạljwʿ)2
 2- (nhdy ḥyạtnạ ạ̹lyk yạ fạdynạ .. dh ạlqlb bḥbk mạ̉swr
 mn ṭybẗ qlbnạ gẖnynạ .. ạ̉ṣl f ḥbk hnạ wsrwr)2
 3- (kl slạm ạ̹ḥnạ lmsnạh .. mdfwʿ tmnh ʿly̱ ạlṣlyb
 nʿlnh llʿạlm yḥyạh .. nʿlnh bạsmk yạ ḥbyb)2</lyrics>
<title>nfrḥ byk yạ msyḥnạ yạ gẖạly</title>
